{"tid":2892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸妹玩手機亂過馬路　遭無牌司機開車撞飛","createTime":"2016-11-26T03:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T15:59:30.000Z","uid":122,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da1aca3260bdcf00e66ed14d7978f6a46622c92d","tid":2892,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>江蘇女玩手機亂過馬路　遭無牌司機開車撞飛</strong><br />\n<br />\n過路時低頭玩手機可釀大禍！江蘇南通市桃園路中南城路段周二晚11時許發生驚險車禍，一名22歲許姓女子在亂過馬路時只顧低頭玩手機，被一輛途經的私家車撞飛，涉事司機事後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n現場畫面可見，許女在過馬路時低頭玩手機，未有注意到私家車從後方駛至，當場被撞飛，在空中翻騰一圈後才跌落地上，畫面驚心動魄。據悉許女被送至南通市第三人民醫院救治，傷勢略有好轉。<br />\n<br />\n而肇事後逃去的曹姓私家車司機，前日中午在家人陪同下投案自首。警方表示，27歲的曹男曾於2012年因吸毒被吊銷駕駛證，目前因無證駕駛被行政拘留。"},{"pid":"02510ed4806268e46a2661f925464ade10ae3e31","tid":2892,"uid":140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2bb786366dc5893ae36eec3631c2e24457e246","tid":2892,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"祝下世再做中國人"},{"pid":"f700e7f8babd85cb73679517629abe518dffab09","tid":2892,"uid":9017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"大陸玩過馬路真係痴線<br />\n佢之前未試過？"},{"pid":"0e5df90d931e4e97fe458b1df2c53bb215622bce","tid":2892,"uid":377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"恭喜大陸又小個廢柴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf4f69620d2958c1887b0622ea53dd3128e159b","tid":2892,"uid":11033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"good job"},{"pid":"fac8fbadde007750b217a2818a3495ac9a3296ed","tid":2892,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"無牌司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633eaec8506a50ee24bdddb108964e21514dc7f3","tid":2892,"uid":2984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"有請小鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6c241148a0c5005ac2f74263b12e2ff3e5f267","tid":2892,"uid":6755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}